---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro'
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy — Wildiney Di Masi" locale="en">

  <!-- Dark header -->
  <div class="relative bg-dark flex items-end pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="w-full px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <a href="/en/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
          Home
        </a>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted font-mono mb-3">Updated May 15, 2025</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-dark-text leading-tight">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Light body -->
  <div class="bg-paper text-ink px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg prose-neutral">

      <h2>1. Data controller</h2>
      <p>Wildiney Di Masi, reachable at <a href="mailto:wildiney@gmail.com">wildiney@gmail.com</a>, is the data controller for personal data collected on this site, in accordance with Brazil's General Data Protection Law (LGPD — Law No. 13,709/2018).</p>

      <h2>2. Data collected and purposes</h2>

      <h3>2.1 Analytics cookies (with your consent)</h3>
      <p>When you accept cookies, we collect anonymous browsing data through:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics (via Google Tag Manager):</strong> pages visited, session duration, traffic source, and navigation behavior. Data processed by Google LLC in the United States.</li>
        <li><strong>Microsoft Clarity:</strong> heatmaps, session recordings, and click tracking. Data processed by Microsoft Corporation in the United States.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Legal basis: consent (LGPD art. 7, I).</p>

      <h3>2.2 Contact form</h3>
      <p>When you submit a message, we collect your name, email address, and message content. This data is transmitted to <a href="https://formsubmit.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">formsubmit.co</a>, which forwards it to the controller's email, and is used solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>
      <p>Legal basis: legitimate interest (LGPD art. 7, IX).</p>

      <h2>3. Data processors</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google LLC</strong> — Google Analytics / Tag Manager. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Microsoft Corporation</strong> — Microsoft Clarity. <a href="https://privacy.microsoft.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>formsubmit.co</strong> — form delivery. <a href="https://formsubmit.co/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy policy</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data retention</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Analytics data: retained per each platform's policy (Google: 14 months default; Clarity: 13 months).</li>
        <li>Contact messages: kept as long as needed to respond and archive the communication.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Your rights (LGPD art. 18)</h2>
      <p>You have the right to confirm processing, access, correct, anonymize, block, or delete your data, request portability, and withdraw consent at any time. To exercise any right, email <a href="mailto:wildiney@gmail.com">wildiney@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>6. Withdrawing consent</h2>
      <p>You can withdraw your analytics consent at any time by clearing site data in your browser settings. Withdrawal does not affect processing carried out prior to the revocation.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:wildiney@gmail.com">wildiney@gmail.com</a>.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-rule">
      <a href="/en/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-ink/50 hover:text-accent uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
        Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</PageLayout>
